			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Ternary precursor</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">三元前驱体</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">NCM811 precursors; NCM622 precursors; NCM523 precursors; NCA precursors</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">NCM811 precursors; NCM622 precursors; NCM523 precursors; NCA precursors</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">Materials production</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Other materials</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">The ternary precursors are the key link between the upstream metal and the downstream cathode material. They can be divided into NCM811 precursors, NCM622 precursors, NCM523 precursors and NCA precursors according to the composition ratio of elements. The ternary precursor is mainly the hydroxide precipitation of nickel, cobalt, manganese (aluminum). The ternary precursor material 523 has high specific capacity and thermal stability, but its balance between cycle performance, thermal stability, rate performance and self-discharge is poor; 622 has good processing performance and high energy density.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">三元前驱体是上游金属和下游阴极材料之间的关键环节。根据元素组成比例，可分为 NCM811 前驱体、NCM622 前驱体、NCM523 前驱体和 NCA 前驱体。三元前驱体主要是镍、钴、锰（铝）的氢氧化物沉淀。三元前驱体材料 523 具有较高的比容量和热稳定性，但其循环性能、热稳定性、速率性能和自放电之间的平衡性较差；622 具有良好的加工性能和较高的能量密度。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>Nickel, Cobalt, Manganese (Aluminum) Hydroxide</sumFormula>
